freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: My left hand is now developing the symptoms of chilblains, which my right hand started to develop after my initial injection. Maybe it's a coincidence, but not sure.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: A few days after each injection I developed tiny red spots beneath the skin on my fingertips. They feel similar to how a tiny splinter feels, and have taken days to a week to go away. Not sure if it's related to the vaccination or not.
Aches, chills, temp began 24 hr after dose given
